Version 47.2.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Distros! Use 48.0.1!

A further fix for Gtk's backwards-incompatible changes.

Version 47.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~

Includes a small workaround for Gtk deciding to break applications, whilst
this should be sufficient to avoid the crash it is recommended to either use
48.0.1 or patch/downgrade Gtk.

